Changes since version 0.2:
--------------------------

  - Added a couple of more sites and disabled Themes.org.
  - Auto-width on columns.
  - UF daily cartoon viewer now downloads the fullsize image.
  - Fixed some changed URLs/syntax in some modules
  - Washing of HTML-entities from some fields.
 

Changes since version 0.1:
--------------------------

  - Left click on headlines spawns a netscape.
  - Right menu on headlines opens a menu with a number of
    options. Some sites has extra options.
  - Added a User Friendly viewer. Shows todays cartoon and headlines
    from the daily static.
  - Other changes I've forgotten.